data.description: This charming 3 bedroom, 1.1 bath ranch has a modern open floorplan, attached 2 car garage, recent improvements, and very convenient location walking distance to the neighborhood park! ~ Large living room/dining room combo with vaulted ceiling and wood laminate flooring ~ Roomy kitchen features plenty of cabinet space, newer countertops, laundry closet, and oversized sliding glass door ~ Spacious primary bedroom with shared full bath ~ Partially enclosed backyard has inviting deck/pergola, newer fencing, and lots of possibilities ~ Recent bathroom updates ~ New hot water heater 2024 ~ New furnace 2021 ~ One block from Elgin High School ~ Easy access to Route 20 ~ Close to all that vibrant downtown Elgin and the bustling Fox River Valley have to offer!
